IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SIGNAL-EXITS-PERFORM-THROUGH.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(30).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE "MISSING-TARGET" TO TARGET-FIELD
SIGNAL HANDLER ON ERROR
DISPLAY "MAIN BEFORE PERFORM"
PERFORM FIRST THROUGH SECOND
DISPLAY "MAIN AFTER PERFORM".

FIRST.
DISPLAY "FIRST BEFORE SIGNAL FAILURE"
GO TO TARGET-FIELD.

SECOND.
DISPLAY "SECOND SHOULD NOT RUN".

HANDLER.
DISPLAY "PERFORM SIGNAL HANDLER"
STOP.
